{
  "id": "class_0054",
  "name": "Plague Warden of the Salted Wards",
  "title_completion": "a Plague Warden of the Salted Wards",
  "flavor_text": "In a city where the air itself carries judgment, you learned to read the miasma like scripture. You do not cure the sickness \u2014 you consecrate it, drawing chalk lines between the living and the lost, then flooding both with brine until only your will remains standing. The quarantine bell is yours to ring.",
